content.p: The Registrar's Department provides a range of professional administrative services to the University. The Department includes: Staff working in the Department deliver services for students and academic Schools and other professional services in all parts of the University in the UK, China and Malaysia. The Departmental Structure page provides more information and links to the Divisions' web pages.
